description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 44, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 88, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 3 for East, 3 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30442-83391-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [88 Votes, Common]
